body:
## What's Changed
* Remove ClusterImpl#isShutdown method by @sashapolo in https://github.com/scalecube/scalecube-cluster/pull/373
* Update parent by @artem-v in https://github.com/scalecube/scalecube-cluster/pull/376

## New Contributors
* @sashapolo made their first contribution in https://github.com/scalecube/scalecube-cluster/pull/373

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/scalecube/scalecube-cluster/compare/2.6.12...2.6.13

Decouple transport implementation (#362).
Reduce logging of the same errors in Transport (#364).
Upgrade to `scalecube-commons` `1.0.17`.
Upgrade to `reactor` `2020.0.10`.

* Updated `reactor` to `2020.0.6`
* Added safe code in   `TransportImpl` and `MetadataStoreImpl`.
* Enhanced error messages all over the places (now error message contains context information in which error had occurred).
* Cleaned code from reactor deprecates (once again). 
* Made `TransportFactory` required configuration  parameter (removed `ServiceLoaderUtil.findFirst()` magic)
* Fixed CI (@segabriel).

## Development

* Upgraded `reactor` -> `2020.0.5`
* Upgraded `netty` -> `4.1.60`
* Fixed deprecations
* Updated scalecube-commons
